  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Constructors
  • Deprecated Fields 
    Field and Description
    com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.FieldType.STRING_TYPE
    As of v3.0.1. Use Text field instead.
    com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.FieldType.UNKNOWN_TYPE
    As of v3.0.1. Use FieldType.NULL_TYPE instead.
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.TupleSchema.compareWithoutRecursion(AbstractTupleSchema)
    Text type is no longer parameterized
    com.ibm.avatar.api.tam.ModuleMetadata.getDependsOn()
    As of v2.1, replaced by ModuleMetadata.getDependentModules()
    com.ibm.avatar.api.DocReader.getDocFieldAcc(String)
    As of v2.1.1, use DocReader.getDocSchema() to get the document schema and then use the appropriate accessor getter
    com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.Tuple.getElement(int)
    Use accessors FieldGetter, or AbstractTupleSchema.getCol(Tuple, int).
    com.ibm.avatar.api.DocReader.getExtViewFieldAcc(String, String)
    As of v2.1.1, use DocReader.getExternalViewSchema(String) to get the external view schema for extViewName and then use the appropriate accessor
    com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.AbstractTupleSchema.getFirstTextCol()
    com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.AbstractTupleSchema.getFirstTextOrSpanCol()
    com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.FieldType.getIsStringType()
    As of v3.0.1, this method is deprecated. Use getIsText() instead.
    com.ibm.avatar.api.DocReader.getLabelAcc()
    As of v2.1.1, use DocReader.getDocSchema() to get the document schema and then use AbstractTupleSchema.spanAcc(String) with parameter "label" to get the label field accessor.
    com.ibm.avatar.api.DocReader.getTextAcc()
    As of v2.1.1, use DocReader.getDocSchema() to get the document schema and then use AbstractTupleSchema.spanAcc(String) with parameter "text" to get the text field accessor.
    com.ibm.avatar.api.tam.DictionaryMetadata.isAllowEmpty()
    As of v3.0.1, use DictionaryMetadata.isRequired() instead
    com.ibm.avatar.api.tam.TableMetadata.isAllowEmpty()
    As of v3.0.1, use TableMetadata.isRequired() instead
    com.ibm.avatar.api.CompileAQLParams.normalizeURI(String)
    This function will be removed in later releases
  • Deprecated Constructors 
    Constructor and Description
    com.ibm.avatar.algebra.datamodel.ScalarList()
    Use ScalarList.makeScalarListFromType(FieldType) instead, to instantiate ScalarList objects with an explicit type for the scalar elements of the list.
